{"tid":1097530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地試過點氹身邊嘅人開心？","createTime":"2019-04-08T12:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T12:40:11.000Z","uid":177082,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e886fc7295c1722225589679d1edb214d2c9522","tid":1097530,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:15:40.000Z","msg":"我講少少先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.打氣Memo Pad<br />\n初中嘅時候有個高中嘅好朋友考DSE <br />\n我買咗疊Memo紙逐張拆出黎畫畫+寫打氣說話 跟住再痴返埋一疊送俾佢 叫佢每日睇一張<br />\n咁到考完就啱啱好睇曬全疊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（不過佢之後同我講佢一次過睇曬全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n2.生日Surprise<br />\n呢個可能有啲普通不過照講啦<br />\n我朋友生日 前一晚我夾埋佢屋企人俾surprise佢<br />\n因為朋友係啲遲起身嘅人<br />\n咁朝早佢妹妹同爸爸媽媽就預先佈置間屋 我就趁佢未起身上佢屋企等佢起身<br />\n佢一出房門就見到個廳掛住啲氣球同大大隻字（佢個名）+生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候我仲拎埋特登為佢整嘅蛋糕出黎 <br />\n佢瞓醒睡眼惺忪咁就好surprise了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 接考試<br />\n男朋友第一科口試 我扮八卦問佢幾點邊度考之後就一直係考場門口等佢（佢完全唔知我會去搵佢）<br />\n由啲人啱啱入去考等咗勁耐都見唔到佢 <br />\n跟住原來佢係最尾考嗰批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等到最後佢終於出黎 打算開機send message搵我嘅時候 我已經係佢面前出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該仲有好多 諗到再講<br />\n你地呢？你地平時點樣氹身邊啲人開心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cf7ab4e5c0c662e6d34dae01d8c79aa41b373d","tid":1097530,"uid":217643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"互射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e669f9d85267eb6f63ff62d3df8c8325412f6c77","tid":1097530,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6cf7ab4e5c0c662e6d34dae01d8c79aa41b373d","tid":1097530,"uid":217643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"互射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"好開心？"},{"pid":"7d13e90d54467fb576fda4ce19940bd5bc00173c","tid":1097530,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"無試過比人氹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b654042c182e193e3caa669bb16f93779f088add","tid":1097530,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d13e90d54467fb576fda4ce19940bd5bc00173c","tid":1097530,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"無試過比人氹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"問緊點氹人開心喎<br />\n唔好淨係諗人地氹唔氹你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cfebe1033266e017c1b0711c9208ad2ad53b46","tid":1097530,"uid":124140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b654042c182e193e3caa669bb16f93779f088add","tid":1097530,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d13e90d54467fb576fda4ce19940bd5bc00173c","tid":1097530,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"無試過比人氹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"問緊點氹人開心喎<br />\n唔好淨係諗人地氹唔氹你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:22:11.000Z","msg":"自己都無果種感覺好難比到人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7c2c8135587f3b7752056a2b1f7144445977c0","tid":1097530,"uid":177082,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"諗到多個<br />\n4. 溫馨小信封<br />\n媽媽生日 我摺咗個小信封 入面裝咗差唔多50條紙條<br />\n全部都係寫媽媽有咩好 同埋我有咩感激媽媽<br />\n叫佢得閒抽幾條出黎睇下"},{"pid":"82c97d61bbab7d84b261b0a977f36ff4d086bc9e","tid":1097530,"uid":177082,"like":0,